cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid enum value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing failure as it does not match any of the allowed choices: none, info, annoying.

du.explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to an invalid format 'invalid_id' will cause identifier parsing error and prevent proper gNB initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB_ID 設定為無效格式 'invalid_id' 會導致識別碼解析錯誤，並阻止正確的 gNB 初始化。
